        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;flowchart LR\n    %% ===== ENTITIES (Squares) =====\n    USERS[\&quot;USERS\&quot;]\n    APPLICANT[\&quot;APPLICANT\&quot;]\n    GRAMA_NILADHARI[\&quot;GRAMA_NILADHARI\&quot;]\n    SAMURDHI_OFFICER[\&quot;SAMURDHI_OFFICER\&quot;]\n    MINISTER[\&quot;MINISTER\&quot;]\n    ADMIN[\&quot;ADMIN\&quot;]\n\n    WELFARE_APPLICATION[\&quot;WELFARE_APPLICATION\&quot;]\n    HOME_VISIT[\&quot;HOME_VISIT\&quot;]\n    MINISTER_APPROVAL[\&quot;MINISTER_APPROVAL\&quot;]\n    PAYMENT[\&quot;SAMURDHI_PAYMENT\&quot;]\n\n    %% ===== IS-A (Trapezoid/Triangle equivalent) =====\n    ISA[\\\&quot;IS-A\&quot;/]\n\n    USERS --- ISA\n    ISA --- APPLICANT\n    ISA --- GRAMA_NILADHARI\n    ISA --- SAMURDHI_OFFICER\n    ISA --- MINISTER\n    ISA --- ADMIN\n\n    %% ===== ATTRIBUTES (Ovals) =====\n    User_ID([\&quot;User_ID (PK)\&quot;])\n    Username([\&quot;Username\&quot;])\n    Password([\&quot;Password\&quot;])\n    Role([\&quot;Role\&quot;])\n    Phone_Num([\&quot;Phone_Num\&quot;])\n\n    USERS --- User_ID\n    USERS --- Username\n    USERS --- Password\n    USERS --- Role\n    USERS --- Phone_Num\n\n    App_ID([\&quot;Application_ID (PK)\&quot;])\n    App_Date([\&quot;Date\&quot;])\n    App_Status([\&quot;Status\&quot;])\n\n    WELFARE_APPLICATION --- App_ID\n    WELFARE_APPLICATION --- App_Date\n    WELFARE_APPLICATION --- App_Status\n\n    Visit_ID([\&quot;Visit_ID (PK)\&quot;])\n    Visit_Date([\&quot;Date\&quot;])\n    Remarks([\&quot;Remarks\&quot;])\n    Recommendation([\&quot;Recommendation\&quot;])\n\n    HOME_VISIT --- Visit_ID\n    HOME_VISIT --- Visit_Date\n    HOME_VISIT --- Remarks\n    HOME_VISIT --- Recommendation\n\n    Req_ID([\&quot;Request_ID (PK)\&quot;])\n    Req_Date([\&quot;Date\&quot;])\n    Req_Status([\&quot;Status\&quot;])\n\n    MINISTER_APPROVAL --- Req_ID\n    MINISTER_APPROVAL --- Req_Date\n    MINISTER_APPROVAL --- Req_Status\n\n    Payment_ID([\&quot;Payment_ID (PK)\&quot;])\n    Amount([\&quot;Amount\&quot;])\n    Payment_Date([\&quot;Date\&quot;])\n    Payment_Status([\&quot;Status\&quot;])\n\n    PAYMENT --- Payment_ID\n    PAYMENT --- Amount\n    PAYMENT --- Payment_Date\n    PAYMENT --- Payment_Status\n\n    %% ===== RELATIONSHIPS (Diamonds) =====\n    SUBMITS{\&quot;Submits\&quot;}\n    CONDUCTS{\&quot;Conducts\&quot;}\n    CHECKS{\&quot;Checks\&quot;}\n    FORWARDS{\&quot;Forwards\&quot;}\n    REVIEWS{\&quot;Reviews\&quot;}\n    GENERATES{\&quot;Generates\&quot;}\n    RECEIVES{\&quot;Receives\&quot;}\n\n    %% ===== CONNECTIONS WITH CARDINALITY =====\n    %% Applicant submits Application\n    APPLICANT ---|1| SUBMITS ---|M| WELFARE_APPLICATION\n\n    %% Officer conducts Home Visit\n    SAMURDHI_OFFICER ---|1| CONDUCTS ---|M| HOME_VISIT\n\n    %% Home Visit related to Application\n    HOME_VISIT ---|1| CHECKS ---|1| WELFARE_APPLICATION\n\n    %% GN forwards Application to Minister\n    GRAMA_NILADHARI ---|1| FORWARDS ---|M| MINISTER_APPROVAL\n    WELFARE_APPLICATION ---|1| FORWARDS\n\n    %% Minister reviews request\n    MINISTER ---|1| REVIEWS ---|M| MINISTER_APPROVAL\n\n    %% Request generates payment\n    MINISTER_APPROVAL ---|1| GENERATES ---|1| PAYMENT\n\n    %% Applicant receives payment\n    APPLICANT ---|1| RECEIVES ---|M| PAYMENT&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="IOa4-MWvAUdTQVhdvQfZ-181">
